HEADWORD: Beseech
<hw>Be*seech"</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Solicitation; supplication.</def>
<mark>[Obs. or Poetic]</mark> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Beseecher</ent>⟦br⟧
